title: President Donald J. Trump Has Mobilized the Full Resources of the Federal Government to Respond to the Coronavirus – The White House
content:
Fact Sheets			

		Healthcare

I will never hesitate to take any necessary steps to protect the lives, health, and safety of the American people. I will always put the wellbeing of America first.
						President Donald J. Trump					MOBILIZING ALL FEDERAL RESOURCES: President Donald J. Trump is leveraging the full power of the Federal Government to protect the health and safety of the American people.
